[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "line": 33,
    "target_en": "\\\"Humph! I'm quite amazed by your dirty deeds, Keiichi-san!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "line": 41,
    "target_en": "\\\"......He is a boy, after all.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "line": 49,
    "target_en": "\\\"Mii-chan, Shii-chan... Keiichi-kun looks confused...... hau...\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "line": 59,
    "target_en": "\\\"Did you hear that, Sis?"
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "line": 62,
    "target_en": " We're not playing tug of war here. Are you trying to tear Kei-chan apart?!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "line": 68,
    "target_en": "\\\"I'm not playing tug of war! You're the one who's stretching him. "
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "line": 75,
    "target_en": "Go back to Okinomiya, Shion!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "line": 81,
    "target_en": "\\\"Okay,"
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "line": 84,
    "target_en": " I will."
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "line": 87,
    "target_en": " Oops.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "line": 102,
    "target_en": "I let go of Keiichi suddenly, so he and Sis flew off like a rubber band."
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "line": 107,
    "target_en": "Keiichi rolled on the ground while Sis was stuck in a bush head-first..."
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "line": 109,
    "target_en": " What lively people."
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "line": 115,
    "target_en": "\\\"See you, Kei-chan."
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "line": 118,
    "target_en": " Sis might assault me if I stick around any longer, so I'll get going.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "line": 126,
    "target_en": "\\\"Oh, Shion..."
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "line": 129,
    "target_en": " uh... thanks for today.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "line": 135,
    "target_en": "\\\"Ah, forget it."
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "line": 138,
    "target_en": " I didn't do much.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "line": 146,
    "target_en": "\\\"See you, Shion.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "line": 151,
    "target_en": "His hand landed"
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "line": 153,
    "target_en": " on my head......"
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "line": 159,
    "target_en": "Rub, rub, rub."
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "line": 164,
    "target_en": "...He stroked my head pretty roughly."
  },
  {
    "id": 25,
    "line": 166,
    "target_en": " But the warmth reminded me......"
  },
  {
    "id": 26,
    "line": 174,
    "target_en": "\\\"Ah, ahahahahaha...!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 27,
    "line": 177,
    "target_en": " Excuse me, I'm going."
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "line": 180,
    "target_en": " See you, Sis!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 29,
    "line": 186,
    "target_en": "\\\"Don't ever come here again!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 30,
    "line": 189,
    "target_en": " Rena, keep your eyes on her!"
  },
  {
    "id": 31,
    "line": 192,
    "target_en": " Satoko, set traps!"
  },
  {
    "id": 32,
    "line": 195,
    "target_en": " Rika-chan, purify this area with salt!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 33,
    "line": 205,
    "target_en": "The warmth remained on the top of my head...... It felt ticklish and... sore."
  },
  {
    "id": 34,
    "line": 210,
    "target_en": "I had to stop... I got off my moped and pushed that aching spot against a telephone pole."
  },
  {
    "id": 35,
    "line": 217,
    "target_en": "I'm sorry, Satoshi-kun. I'm sorry!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 36,
    "line": 219,
    "target_en": " I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 37,
    "line": 224,
    "target_en": "I never forgot about you... I still remember you..."
  },
  {
    "id": 38,
    "line": 229,
    "target_en": "I'm worthless without you... I can't stand life without you because it's gray and cold and boring..."
  },
  {
    "id": 39,
    "line": 231,
    "target_en": " It's true... it's true..."
  },
  {
    "id": 40,
    "line": 236,
    "target_en": "I can never smile because you aren't here... I can't..."
  },
  {
    "id": 41,
    "line": 246,
    "target_en": "\\\"See you, Shion.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 42,
    "line": 251,
    "target_en": "Keiichi's face appeared in my mind."
  },
  {
    "id": 43,
    "line": 256,
    "target_en": "...I recalled the touch of his hand stroking my head..."
  },
  {
    "id": 44,
    "line": 261,
    "target_en": "It wasn't warm!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 45,
    "line": 266,
    "target_en": "I wasn't happy!"
  },
  {
    "id": 46,
    "line": 271,
    "target_en": "It was rough and painful!"
  },
  {
    "id": 47,
    "line": 276,
    "target_en": "I hate that insensitive guy!"
  },
  {
    "id": 48,
    "line": 281,
    "target_en": "He's too childish, rude, and cold! He's like a stray dog!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 49,
    "line": 286,
    "target_en": "I wasn't happy! It wasn't warm!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 50,
    "line": 288,
    "target_en": " I wasn't happy or overjoyed at all..."
  },
  {
    "id": 51,
    "line": 297,
    "target_en": "\\\"Noooooo!!!! ...Oohhh... Satoshi... kun..."
  },
  {
    "id": 52,
    "line": 300,
    "target_en": " Ooohhh... wahhhhhh...\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 53,
    "line": 309,
    "target_en": "...............Mmph..."
  },
  {
    "id": 54,
    "line": 314,
    "target_en": "Satoshi-kun mumbled."
  },
  {
    "id": 55,
    "line": 319,
    "target_en": "...He didn't know what to say in a situation like this."
  },
  {
    "id": 56,
    "line": 325,
    "target_en": "......But he knew that he had better say something."
  },
  {
    "id": 57,
    "line": 330,
    "target_en": " ...He wanted to say something..."
  },
  {
    "id": 58,
    "line": 335,
    "target_en": " ...but he didn't know what to say..."
  },
  {
    "id": 59,
    "line": 337,
    "target_en": " so, he just mumbled..."
  },
  {
    "id": 60,
    "line": 342,
    "target_en": "I'm sorry...... Shion."
  },
  {
    "id": 61,
    "line": 347,
    "target_en": "Why are you apologizing, Satoshi-kun...?"
  },
  {
    "id": 62,
    "line": 352,
    "target_en": "I'm the one who should apologize."
  },
  {
    "id": 63,
    "line": 357,
    "target_en": "Even though I said I'd wait for you...... even though I believed my heart wouldn't change......"
  },
  {
    "id": 64,
    "line": 362,
    "target_en": "......My heart is full of holes."
  },
  {
    "id": 65,
    "line": 368,
    "target_en": "......You're leaking out from the small cracks in my heart, little by little......"
  },
  {
    "id": 66,
    "line": 373,
    "target_en": "......You're leaking out... from me......!"
  },
  {
    "id": 67,
    "line": 378,
    "target_en": "......Are you suffering because I'm here...?"
  },
  {
    "id": 68,
    "line": 383,
    "target_en": "Wh-Why...?!"
  },
  {
    "id": 69,
    "line": 385,
    "target_en": " You're so precious to me..."
  },
  {
    "id": 70,
    "line": 390,
    "target_en": "So, don't say that...!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 71,
    "line": 395,
    "target_en": "...I've been here with you all this time."
  },
  {
    "id": 72,
    "line": 398,
    "target_en": " ........."
  },
  {
    "id": 73,
    "line": 401,
    "target_en": "But..."
  },
  {
    "id": 74,
    "line": 406,
    "target_en": " I think I'm hurting you"
  },
  {
    "id": 75,
    "line": 411,
    "target_en": " by continuing to exist..."
  },
  {
    "id": 76,
    "line": 413,
    "target_en": " I don't want that."
  },
  {
    "id": 77,
    "line": 418,
    "target_en": "That's not true...... No, no, no!!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 78,
    "line": 420,
    "target_en": " Where have you been, Satoshi-kun?!"
  },
  {
    "id": 79,
    "line": 422,
    "target_en": " You weren't with me!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 80,
    "line": 424,
    "target_en": " Tell me where you are! "
  },
  {
    "id": 81,
    "line": 427,
    "target_en": "What's the address? What's the postal code? What's the name of the city? What's the street number?!"
  },
  {
    "id": 82,
    "line": 429,
    "target_en": " Tell me...!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 83,
    "line": 434,
    "target_en": ".....................There isn't"
  },
  {
    "id": 84,
    "line": 439,
    "target_en": " an address..."
  },
  {
    "id": 85,
    "line": 444,
    "target_en": "............Ahahahahahaha."
  },
  {
    "id": 86,
    "line": 449,
    "target_en": "......I knew it......"
  },
  {
    "id": 87,
    "line": 454,
    "target_en": "...Telling me you've always been with me, always by my side... That's such a cliche........."
  },
  {
    "id": 88,
    "line": 456,
    "target_en": " Ahahahahaha........."
  },
  {
    "id": 89,
    "line": 461,
    "target_en": "Which do you prefer, Shion...?"
  },
  {
    "id": 90,
    "line": 466,
    "target_en": "...If I can give you strength, I'll stay by your side forever......"
  },
  {
    "id": 91,
    "line": 468,
    "target_en": " but if you're suffering because of me, I'll disappear right away."
  },
  {
    "id": 92,
    "line": 474,
    "target_en": "\\\"......Don't say that......"
  },
  {
    "id": 93,
    "line": 477,
    "target_en": " I want to be with you... always..."
  },
  {
    "id": 94,
    "line": 480,
    "target_en": " I want to be with you... forever...\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 95,
    "line": 486,
    "target_en": "Okay..."
  },
  {
    "id": 96,
    "line": 488,
    "target_en": " I'll stay with you then."
  },
  {
    "id": 97,
    "line": 495,
    "target_en": "A car passed by."
  },
  {
    "id": 98,
    "line": 501,
    "target_en": "The noise snapped me out of my reverie."
  },
  {
    "id": 99,
    "line": 507,
    "target_en": "\\\"...Huff..."
  },
  {
    "id": 100,
    "line": 510,
    "target_en": " huff.........\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 101,
    "line": 515,
    "target_en": "...The sky was turning orange."
  },
  {
    "id": 102,
    "line": 520,
    "target_en": "I should get home before it gets cold......"
  },
  {
    "id": 103,
    "line": 522,
    "target_en": " I should go home, to Okinomiya."
  },
  {
    "id": 104,
    "line": 528,
    "target_en": "......You're with me, right...?"
  },
  {
    "id": 105,
    "line": 530,
    "target_en": " Are you with me right now... Satoshi-kun...?"
  },
  {
    "id": 106,
    "line": 537,
    "target_en": "I walked back to my moped."
  },
  {
    "id": 107,
    "line": 542,
    "target_en": "...My feet sank into the grass..."
  },
  {
    "id": 108,
    "line": 544,
    "target_en": " Crunch crunch crunch..."
  },
  {
    "id": 109,
    "line": 551,
    "target_en": "I stopped when I reached my bike."
  },
  {
    "id": 110,
    "line": 557,
    "target_en": "...But then I heard"
  },
  {
    "id": 111,
    "line": 559,
    "target_en": " an extra footstep."
  },
  {
    "id": 112,
    "line": 565,
    "target_en": "I gasped..."
  },
  {
    "id": 113,
    "line": 567,
    "target_en": " I could feel somebody else's presence."
  },
  {
    "id": 114,
    "line": 573,
    "target_en": "I'm not stupid."
  },
  {
    "id": 115,
    "line": 579,
    "target_en": "Nobody else was around here."
  },
  {
    "id": 116,
    "line": 584,
    "target_en": "Nobody had suddenly appeared behind me."
  },
  {
    "id": 117,
    "line": 590,
    "target_en": ".........So I wasn't surprised to find nobody"
  },
  {
    "id": 118,
    "line": 595,
    "target_en": " when I turned around."
  },
  {
    "id": 119,
    "line": 600,
    "target_en": "But..."
  },
  {
    "id": 120,
    "line": 605,
    "target_en": " he was definitely"
  },
  {
    "id": 121,
    "line": 610,
    "target_en": " still there."
  },
  {
    "id": 122,
    "line": 618,
    "target_en": "\\\"...Satoshi-kun.........\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 123,
    "line": 623,
    "target_en": "I couldn't see him...... but he was there......"
  },
  {
    "id": 124,
    "line": 625,
    "target_en": " He was there for me."
  },
  {
    "id": 125,
    "line": 630,
    "target_en": "Satoshi-kun never lies."
  },
  {
    "id": 126,
    "line": 636,
    "target_en": "......He said he'd be with me all the time......"
  },
  {
    "id": 127,
    "line": 641,
    "target_en": "...I'd just been too insensitive to feel his existence until now."
  },
  {
    "id": 128,
    "line": 647,
    "target_en": "\\\"Satoshi-kun........."
  },
  {
    "id": 129,
    "line": 652,
    "target_en": " ...Satoshi-kun...\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 130,
    "line": 657,
    "target_en": "A breeze tickled my hair."
  },
  {
    "id": 131,
    "line": 663,
    "target_en": "...It felt cold"
  },
  {
    "id": 132,
    "line": 668,
    "target_en": " ...but..."
  },
  {
    "id": 133,
    "line": 673,
    "target_en": " to me, it was nothing but the warmth of his hand..."
  },
  {
    "id": 134,
    "line": 679,
    "target_en": "It took me a while to notice that my cheeks were wet with tears..."
  }
]